\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 # DSP ObjectList AutoUpdater \emdash  User Guide (v1.2)\par
\par
Author: DSP PM Team\par
Version: 1.2\par
\par
## PURPOSE\par
\par
Automate building and maintaining DSP ObjectLists from Active Directory using a JSON policy.\par
v1.2 adds **Scope.Exclude** and expands operator support. No runtime behavior changes after the AD query.\par
\par
1. WHAT YOU GET IN THE ZIP\par
\par
---\par
\par
DSPObjectListAutoUpdater\par
\f1\u9474?\f2   DSPObjectListAutoUpdater.ps1        (Main runner)\par
\f1\u9474?\f2   README\\_v1.2\\_UserGuide.rtf           (This document)\par
\f1\u9474?\f2\par
\f1\u9500?\u9472?\f2 Config\par
\f1\u9474?\f2   ExamplePolicy\\_\\*.json                (Ready-to-use sample policies)\par
\f1\u9474?\f2\par
